<plot>A very basic look at the creation of the film What Lies Beneath (2000) that delves more into the film's director, Robert Zemeckis, than the movie itself. We are basically given information about Zemeckis' career with clips from his past films and interviews with actors who took part in his films. A look at the film's 'Hitchcock-esque' direction is also brought to our attention, to show how this thriller was pulled off.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?651811</url></doc>
